:924461,"uid":49197,"like":44,"dislike":2,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T06:44:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/a8/Set_subsetAofB.svg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fa%2Fa8%2FSet_subsetAofB.svg&h=792cfac8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\na=跳樓<br />\nb=墜樓<br />\n跳樓=自殺<br />\n墜樓=自殺/他殺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T11:01:21.000Z","msg":"仲有失足"},{"pid":"8b53ea3a733a0aabf714816b8941a04d1b5d7c36","tid":924461,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38d9c4a0229ac1db340a4cc2fab696d581d9a51b","tid":924461,"uid":215634,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T07:31:02.000Z","msg":"原因有二：<br />\n1. 同法醫驗屍/法庭用字既要求一樣，要確切精準，唔可以有猜疑空間，無證據下假定死者完全係出於自願跳樓。同埋因為兒家出新聞要同其他媒體鬥快，但係又唔想後來發現自己炒車，將推人落樓/其他意外變成自殺，只能夠用「墮樓」<br />\n<br />\n2.同上面所講一樣，想淡化對社會影響。但係大家都心照啦，香港周不時都有人自殺，大家都習以為常。其實淡唔淡化都無所謂。反正政府都唔會做野，一係就派海馬公園飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T13:42:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cebe758f49f209c7d8be83218998ff09e046d1b","tid":924461,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1da91ec0724a4d8f815ebad76370de06b16ca406","tid":924461,"uid":152262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3849af03c0f07838d7138d466c05ec53dba1044e","tid":924461,"uid":82917,"like":155,"dislike":13,"score":142,"quote":{"pid":"ee759d63fbec73320778de2076f34612f765ccd2","tid":924461,"uid":47674,"like":304,"dislike":5,"score":299,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T06:34:50.000Z","msg":"跳樓 係主動尋死<br />\n墮樓 可以係自殺 他殺 或意外<br />\n你點知佢跌落嚟嘅原因係咩？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T06:35:41.000Z","msg":"原來無墨水既人係小美我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src